:0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T00:14:29.000Z","msg":"紅嘅賺返一兩年都夠錢退休過世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n未到中年已經可以退休<br />\n當然講緊外國個堆<br />\n香港始終人少 可能要賺多四五年先夠退休過世<br />\n<br />\n大把YouTuber賺夠錢就開始追下夢想<br />\n追下追下發埋達都得"},{"pid":"32e91f6cbe70396a80d1f8a139cd90676959af63","tid":764253,"uid":18040,"like":90,"dislike":1,"score":89,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T00:23:18.000Z","msg":"中年vlog <br />\n中年人愛用品<br />\n變成中年人後心態<br />\n中年人 vs 年青人<br />\n中年人get ready with me<br />\n中年人淘寶開箱<br />\n跟中年人過一天"},{"pid":"c50374bd39f6e30d478a935f9ebbcfc3d02d5260","tid":764253,"uid":17103,"like":4,"dislike":8,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"18422f7796a5fb0e0a65b3f3c9893d4b21fe33be","tid":764253,"uid":29093,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T23:51:59.000Z","msg":"人地一早賺左 你打工 20 - 30 年儲既錢 <br />\n<br />\n只要唔大駛,  佢地根本半退休都夠啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T00:34:07.000Z","msg":"如果你無一技之長, 呢世都要怕無晒 D 錢 (被人呃, 病, 投資失利 ... )<br />\n<br />\n做得呢 D 其實同其他工種都無差, 去到中年兢爭力大減.<br />\n2x - 3x 一定要做好晒準備, 如果到 4x 供得甩層樓.  無得撈做下掃地看更起馬唔洗訓街.<br />\n<br />\n呢個世界未到 7x 都唔洗諗退休, 當你人到 30 搵到三千萬, 你識唔識點 Keep 都成問題. <br />\n大把奸搞既人會謀撚住你 D 錢.  男女都色誘扮 Friend 投資大亨叫你上車."},{"pid":"509d6f9db2c8bcddd102e2c3bd0310c73434a9d7","tid":764253,"uid":46700,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"8ce47d3922aa3de1c7784533c4eef36bea1f3975","tid":764253,"uid":65400,"like":89,"dislike":2,"score":87,"quote":{"pid":"3d1b82bf20fd4f93f853d6b27dedd1876b5d7698","tid":764253,"uid":27251,"like":43,"dislike":5,"score":38,"quote":{"pid":"66db8ca7c2ca5d4e3f9e6f097e47ceca1b37a894","tid":764253,"uid":58140,"like":2,"dislike":67,"score":-65,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T20:49:12.000Z","msg":"隻屎xx咪係成功代表"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T20:55:28.000Z","msg":"成功既...佢出果啲垃圾真係有人買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-01T23:23:40.000Z","msg":"點睇eminleo先係最成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T00:38:21.000Z","msg":"假假地都政協<br />\n你估流架？"},{"pid":"d9f79cd75d2f36a4abd5ff6688e58bcd82017906","tid":764253,"uid":161935,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T00:39:59.000Z","msg":"唔少youtuber本身有技能，唔拍片都搵到食。<br />\n不過佢地見到當年youtube個趨勢，咪食住條水搵幾年錢，好彩紅到的話真係可以提早退休。<br />\n咪以為人地拍開箱/gameplay 鳩下鳩下就無計劃，佢養成左一班觀眾群，建立到慣性收視既時候，出啲垃圾片cap水好過整啲所謂高汁片啦。你估真係為夢想為左提供娛樂比觀眾咩。"},{"pid":"c9bd8951c7521cea654f2ca380ce0eaeb8465659","tid":764253,"uid":34771,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T00:46:05.000Z","msg":"參考窮飛龍"},{"pid":"b2b9ad9b0d37f9b88e3461bb266cd446a39becc5","tid":764253,"uid":11448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T00:49:32.000Z","msg":"唔需你擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大j書展出下帽同tee又撈一筆了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e203bec1e96da795130780aa7643978e9847706","tid":764253,"uid":72228,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"d9f79cd75d2f36a4abd5ff6688e58bcd82017906","tid":764253,"uid":161935,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T00:39:59.000Z","msg":"唔少youtuber本身有技能，唔拍片都搵到食。<br />\n不過佢地見到當年youtube個趨勢，咪食住條水搵幾年錢，好彩紅到的話真係可以提早退休。<br />\n咪以為人地拍開箱/gameplay 鳩下鳩下就無計劃，佢養成左一班觀眾群，建立到慣性收視既時候，出啲垃圾片cap水好過整啲所謂高汁片啦。你估真係為夢想為左提供娛樂比觀眾咩。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T00:51:08.000Z","msg":"樓主以為自己好醒架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但班youtuber都唔撚係蠢<br />\n咪以為做youtube果班係傻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1d8eecc5c35ab60e47f347e46b6183d6117ff0a","tid":764253,"uid":149572,"like":5,"dislike":10,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"4e54e9f651f81b9511d4e73d6c7833ebe0cd5f25","tid":764253,"uid":15371,"like":175,"dislike":7,"score":168,"quote"